org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.driver.js

Class JSSourceFileHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.driver.js.JSSourceFileHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISourceFileHandler

    public final class JSSourceFileHandler
extends Object
implements ISourceFileHandler
    Implementation of ISourceFileHandler that constructs ASCompilationUnit's. JSSourceFileHandler is the SourceFileHandler that provides JSCompilationUnit for *.as files. JSDriver registers JSSourceFileHandler at FlexApplicationProject. This implementation is part of FalconJS. For more details on FalconJS see org.apache.flex.compiler.JSDriver
